    <!-- Walkthrough / Tutorial -->
    <string name="walkthrough_title_1">1. Zoom &amp; Presets</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_body_1">Use the slider or quick buttons to zoom the image. Digital zoom automatically kicks in beyond the hardware limit.</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_title_2">2. Filters &amp; Sharpening</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_body_2">On the Filters and Adjustment tabs, you can improve text readability with accessibility color filters, contrast, and sharpening.</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_title_3">3. Freeze &amp; Save</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_body_3">Use the large center button to freeze the image for comfortable reading. You can save or share the enhanced image with others.</string>
